## Repo-wide ignores (minimal)

# OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDEs/editors
.idea/
.vs/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json

# PlatformIO (root firmware project)
.pio/

# Local secrets
.env*
!.env.example
**/*secrets*.*
**/*credentials*.*

# Private keys / certs (if they ever appear)
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
